ly considering the writeObject method would still involve byte arrays. I need to be careful with this approach!\n\n**Considering serialization challenges**\n\nI’m thinking about using `org.bouncycastle.asn1.pkcs.PrivateKeyInfo`, but it’s not serializable. Using `java.util.Date` with bytes seems impossible without a carrier. Maybe I can look into Bouncy's `JournaledAlgorithm` as a carrier, but then again, a static map might not work. It feels like we could be okay with a one-to-one mapping of the active class file. I wonder if we really need to run tests after all. Let’s keep this concise!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_09089e63592d3bce0169fbb83ae89881a2af8893e00eca5408\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp-7hFAFzsVM8lX7x7O_cxX8ckybt-2hB9je6juybagesD1M4D75HJlNdFFM865b_zwP_x-hybFQzTKN_bAj2PXfR3By__8mNKSCiGYFP6zS0nF6ZXZgPTva7egbhQPnVgXPh11qXkeHNyGU5xnokUaltZcJ6CZHWyPdZADh9VixHfMC8Fczaz8Cc1ntuMPMwCkKvaA4Lk32wDQ_nZjDqE2ShbSq-hf8QtgHcLi06t8KtCvsiHJXe9FaqVh_6WOTd8IfHbqSNblY_57lCiZ7BfZ5Gv7wHaLzV6WUE0081u9n2GFScOxXRPudajQRjpKDE5KQohC6xEpijKL-FRGmb5uSFk-4D8szPjJRY6xBLjWXv7JuBAEHOmmGEOpNCK7hN_p3sRYazvsBJhM2GdKXeq_d186SQFerKDAODJ4Sz2YZTkH4Mktce17ZjQzXzQ8km_aUmGMjZk8F9W5RBZz3Y3fNfGG3_ohnlFkCB_cxkQ1WRaTM1zcuWqLTDkHf3Nqgnp6jHnfO_LFAhSy9aC2E4Ki66288C3vYZ586Ehv2i4xcwmtnF6Y-1zXSCim3370seYJxhNSqqbonuNKCJLQsiPBwy6C7wXhxEEUGOX1XKkr5ll3_E7AIMywYp3k0R_YGf8o0JZte3z64Byki8OL_y_GMVO_joaYXfwNWXoBcseuyO-AUVzYxkwVWHJs5peGePkgyVsBW6wieefQYmP8M-z6ByCOQ0sMzbye7DhqVxx9k9Ljb4FpWMeHgECgosD2E2VdIfnpWa9MsyYgFgyYxCM7yS1OzosM2iVfpyIR_zGi3vsKraOsnSF1l0Zv3g2x7Co8ZaAvHig3ene9KnLr-D12WlaIj6vClq6ufDYrkZw1HlVC7ooTBn_xZgOO7D4FZopGfH1vvwoCbYnK02XygPCK6bb6sfh2tODbeHeOcUFm15aEHWrAL90mNcjWkbWwfm0x1xaMaTnhJZmPUDAVkm1AVX1Zh4DVG06gf46cmSJauySuGGcAlTTKLzAbFtzVHa4UGPEnr9S-HkNb6e5ooP2HYMbuwN96SQGozFvPwZ6WNi1K5u2ulDnRlE3so5S43kahG0ZOkhw0N3dce_FPhztCs1SeMNA_vsKouvmffEISmHR-vrc87MY2nAtbvFfUGcQxVBkfb9PKDsT4_cXPOwDzQae8JOEQbogAhxmzGop5rJrDeLZfleNEShhERS01GdMxc86A0v3pJuTBzjTuJg_i6JfmhoXd6UBzewscl0nI3k